{"tid":710090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人] 嘉希隊長進軍職業球壇　成為中國第1人","createTime":"2018-06-20T13:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T14:06:40.000Z","uid":23451,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d945f6eb53d9e979d545583781ea0c3ee07e72de","tid":710090,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180620/mobile/bkn-20180620165107563-0620_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180620%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180620165107563-0620_00882_001.html&d=GNMrYXnoROGLfIcRfWQGKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=58e8afe7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180620/mobile/bkn-20180620165107563-0620_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/20/G3pAq7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2FG3pAq7.png&h=6919e42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港又有運動員進軍職業！香港女子棍網球代表隊隊長許嘉希獲女子職業棍球網聯賽(Women Professional Lacrosse League)隊伍巴爾的摩英勇(Baltimore Brave)邀請加盟，成為首位香港及中國的職業棍網球員。她將於香港時間6月24日凌晨2時(美國東岸時間6月23日下午2時) 為巴爾的摩首次上陣，球迷可以在網上觀賞比賽直播 <a href=\"https://laxallstars.com/wpll/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flaxallstars.com%2Fwpll%2F&d=GNMrYXnoROGLfIcRfWQGKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=98b74415\" target=\"_blank\">https://laxallstars.com/wpll/</a>　 <br />\n<br />\nWPLL既是職業聯賽又是女子棍網球新星的發展計劃。5支參賽伍集合了世界最佳女子棍網球球員。WPLL首個賽季於今年6月開始。隨著許嘉希的加盟，香港成為繼澳洲、加拿大、英國、意大利、墨西哥、南韓及美國之後，第8個參與WPLL的國家及地區。 <br />\n<br />\n作為隊長及一位進攻球員，許嘉希在2017年女子棍網球世界盃表現優秀，在8場港隊的比賽中取得9個入球（隊中排名第4）、5次助攻（隊中排名第2）、贏得11次爭發球(draw controls)（隊中排名第2），6次令對手失誤(caused turnovers) (隊中第二多）。 巴爾的摩球隊總經理Jessy Morgan在今年一月訪港指導港隊訓練時，已對許嘉希的技術及領導能力留下深刻印象，相信她可以為WPLL對來正面影響。他指出：「香港隊有一批出色的球員，他們每天都在不斷進步。在2013年的世界盃，他們取得了1勝4負的成績，但去年他們已能夠提高到4勝4負。他們的冒起證明棍網球運動在世界持續發展及茁壯成長。嘉希是一位具領袖風範的球員，對棍網球運動專注認真，很高興今年初可以與她合作，我期待今個夏天再次與她合作。我有信心她會為巴爾的摩作出貢獻，同時亦希望她可以將在這裏學到的東西帶回香港。」 <br />\n<br />\n在美國期間，許嘉希除了參與WPLL的賽事及訓練，更會為當地的青年棍網球計劃擔任教練，希望透過WPLL全面的棍網球體驗，讓她以及香港代表隊繼續進步。目前巴爾的摩在WPLL以兩戰全勝暫列聯賽榜首，他們分別以20:12及15:10擊敗 Philadelphia Fire以及New England Command。嘉希將會在6月23日代表巴爾的摩上陣，面對New York Fight。如欲了解更多WPLL的資訊以及比賽賽程，可瀏覽<a href=\"https://www.prowomenslax.com/gameschedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prowomenslax.com%2Fgameschedule&d=GNMrYXnoROGLfIcRfWQGKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=40b26a66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.prowomenslax.com/gameschedule</a>"},{"pid":"57fa2fe5813b28cccd211aeab593110cc1a6ed8e","tid":710090,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047771a857efdc158e7a53805b81e0de39aa54c3","tid":710090,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9100b05545f14dd67cb96f79628ab2ba1d17e3aa","tid":710090,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dc0fa1aa592c4f192d5526692d823f2df8b1a9","tid":710090,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"關中國撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又認親認戚"},{"pid":"421fdcf26450977f6583d2237eb8e236522cb554","tid":710090,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32dc0fa1aa592c4f192d5526692d823f2df8b1a9","tid":710090,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"關中國撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又認親認戚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=GNMrYXnoROGLfIcRfWQGKS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=50ccf839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n大家明啦"}]}